[H1]Installation Settings:

[H2]Install ROCm
  Enable/Disable the inclusion of ROCm components as part of the
  installation.

[H2]ROCm Device
  Select ROCm device/component configuration.

[H2]ROCm Component List
  List all ROCm components included in the ROCm install.

[H2]ROCm Install Path
  The location on the system where ROCm components will be installed.

[H1]Maintenance:

[H2]Uninstall ROCm
  Uninstall runfile-based ROCm installation. This is not available
  for package installed ROCm.